item.title: About
item.description: Connor Martin is a software engineer who has a passion for supporting the open source community. Connor currently works at Anaconda, inc. where he is an engineer on the distribution team. He primarily focuses on build system automation and is a core maintainer of conda. In his spare time, Connor likes to find new bars and restaurants to explore and enjoys riding his bike around town. Reach out on GitHub, LinkedIn, or via Email!
